{"id":147192,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/【图集】2010年度最佳图片奖获奖图片/","date":"2011-04-24T18:28:11Z","modified":"2011-04-24T18:28:11Z","title":"【图集】2010&quot;年度最佳图片&quot;奖获奖图片","content":"<p><p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-13164602\">Pictures of the Year: Winning images from 2010</a><br />译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/163202\">surestar</a></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210424_85001.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span>历史悠久的美国摄影奖项“年度最佳图片”正在展示2010年度最佳新闻照片。4月22日，在华盛顿新闻博物馆揭幕的最佳图片展中，就有上图这幅Steve Winter拍摄的小老虎照片。</span></p>\n<div><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210409_35255.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></div>\n<div><span>上图中，陆军中士Brian Keith在开赴阿富汗之前，与妻子及襁褓中的孩子作最后告别，凭借这张照片，《纽约时报》的Damon Winter荣获年度最佳新闻摄影师。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210443_33567.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>上图中，曼谷反政府抗议者在往一辆燃烧的汽车上扔轮胎，凭借这张照片，自由摄影师Athit Perawongmetha赢得现场新闻摄影类头奖。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210403_99127.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>《洛杉矶时报》的Barbara Davidson捕捉到了上图这一瞬间：一位悼念者在Aaron Shannon Jr的葬礼上放飞鸽子，万圣节时，5岁的Shannon在他后院展示新的蜘蛛人装束时，被一名犯罪团伙成员射杀。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210436_55188.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>上图中，一群巴基斯坦人不顾一切要逃离洪水，抓住运送食物供应的军队直升机死死不放，凭借这张照片，路透社的Latif赢得年度最佳自由摄影师。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210433_32607.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>《时代》杂志的Marco Grob凭借上图这张流行天后Lady Gaga的照片，夺得肖像摄影类季军。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210406_87316.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>上图中，澳大利亚俯式冰橇队队员Emma Lincoln-Smith在训练备战2010年冬季奥运会，凭借这张照片，《每日邮报》的Gregg Porteous赢得体育专题摄影类头奖。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210429_19842.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>Palani Mohan凭借上图这张照片，夺得肖像类摄影冠军。图中，印度加尔各答的人力车夫Mohamed Salim拉着人和货物穿过狭窄的城市街道，这一职业也被诟病为“人马”。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210436_70208.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>上图中，奔马逃离冰岛喷发的火山，凭借这张照片，自由摄影师Etienne De Malglaive获得现场新闻摄影类优秀奖。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210400_88904.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>凭借抓拍的这张NBA西部决赛照片，《洛杉矶时报》的Wally Skalij赢得体育组合摄影类优秀奖。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210425_42555.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>上图是“深水地平线”钻井平台坍塌时，附近船只上一名工作人员所拍摄到的照片，凭借它，《纽约时报》获得视觉冲击摄影类优秀奖。为了保护拍摄者，《纽约时报》拒绝透露他的身份。</span></div>\n<p><span><br /> </span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-04/23/20110423210450_87033.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> </span></p>\n<div><span>上图中，在海地太子港市中心街头，一对年轻情侣在一片废墟中独行，自由摄影师Jan Grarup凭借此张照片夺得一般新闻图片故事类冠军。</span></div>\n<div><span><br /> </span></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/163202/189364#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p>\n<p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/143929/189431?from=rss_related\">一周新闻回顾</a></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/66190/189439?from=rss_related\">游戏房</a></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/185202/189321?from=rss_related\">卫报图说24小时（2011.4.22）</a></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/214865/188973?from=rss_related\">惊骇的美丽：俯瞰工业污染</a></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/214096/189245?from=rss_related\">当沙漠染上迷幻色彩</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/504046922/yeeyan/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/163202/189364\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan/504046922/art01.html\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan/504046922/art01.gif\"></a></p>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[]}